reviewText: Master builder takes a team to Israel with new tech to X-ray Herod's Temple Wall and Herod's Place Fortress. He is amazed at the size and wonders if it is even possible with modern tech and equipment.

THIS WAS OUR FIRST DOCUMENTARY ABOUT JERUSALEM AND WAS A GOOD START. HAVE TO GO LOOKING FOR MORE. VERY WELL DONE. THE TIME SCANNERS SERIES HAS BEEN VERY INFORMATIVE AND FASCINATING TO SAY THE LEAST. HOPE THEY COME OUT WITH MORE.
